        "question": "平面向量 $\\vec{a}, \\vec{b}$ 夹角为 $\\frac{\\pi}{3}$，若 $|\\vec{a}|, |\\vec{b}|, |\\vec{a} + \\vec{b}|$ 依次成等差数列，求 $|\\vec{a}|:|\\vec{b}|:|\\vec{a} + \\vec{b}|$。",
        "solution": [
            "设 $|\\vec{a}| = x$，$|\\vec{b}| = y$，$|\\vec{a} + \\vec{b}| = z$",
            "则 $z^{2} = x^{2} + y^{2} + 2xy\\cos \\frac{\\pi}{3} = x^{2} + y^{2} + xy$",
            "由等差数列性质：$2y = x + z$，即 $(2y - x)^{2} = z^{2}$",
            "$\\Rightarrow 4y^{2} + x^{2} - 4xy = x^{2} + y^{2} + xy$",
            "$\\Rightarrow 3y^{2} = 5xy$",
            "$\\Rightarrow y = \\frac{5}{3}x$",
            "$\\Rightarrow z^{2} = x^{2} + \\frac{25}{9}x^{2} + \\frac{5}{3}x^{2} = \\frac{49}{9}x^{2}$",
            "$\\Rightarrow z = \\frac{7}{3}x$",
            "所以 $x:y:z = 3:5:7$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$3:5:7$"],
