        "question": "如图所示，在平面直角坐标系中，椭圆 $\\Gamma: \\frac{x^{2}}{2} + y^{2} = 1$ 的左、右焦点分别为 $F_{1}, F_{2}$，设 $P$ 是第一象限内 $\\Gamma$ 上一点，$PF_{1}, PF_{2}$ 的延长线分别交 $\\Gamma$ 于点 $Q_{1}(x_{1}, y_{1}), Q_{2}(x_{2}, y_{2})$，求 $y_{1} - y_{2}$ 的最大值。<img_a7300f5668be73654cc043aad184115994a8493f66fcb4ae354316c87c6c1861>",
        "solution": [
            "设 $P(s, t)$，则 $k_{PF_{1}} = \\frac{t}{s + 1} \\Rightarrow PF_{1}: x = \\frac{s + 1}{t}y - 1$",
            "联立 $\\begin{cases} x = \\frac{s + 1}{t}y - 1 \\\\ x^{2} + 2y^{2} = 2 \\end{cases} \\Rightarrow \\frac{2s + 3}{t^{2}}y^{2} - \\frac{2(s + 1)}{t}y - 1 = 0$",
            "$\\Rightarrow y_{1} = -\\frac{t}{3 + 2s}$",
            "同理，$PF_{2}: x = \\frac{s - 1}{t}y + 1$，联立 $\\begin{cases} x = \\frac{s - 1}{t}y + 1 \\\\ x^{2} + 2y^{2} = 2 \\end{cases}$",
            "$\\Rightarrow \\frac{-2s + 3}{t^{2}}y^{2} + \\frac{2(s - 1)}{t}y - 1 = 0$",
            "$\\Rightarrow y_{2} = -\\frac{t}{3 - 2s}$",
            "于是 $y_{1} - y_{2} = \\frac{t}{3 - 2s} - \\frac{t}{3 + 2s} = \\frac{4st}{9 - 4s^{2}}$",
            "设 $s = \\sqrt{2}\\cos \\theta$，$t = \\sin \\theta$，$\\theta \\in (0, \\frac{\\pi}{2})$",
            "则 $y_{1} - y_{2} = \\frac{4\\sqrt{2}\\sin \\theta \\cos \\theta}{9 - 8\\cos^{2}\\theta} = \\frac{4\\sqrt{2}\\sin \\theta \\cos \\theta}{9\\sin^{2}\\theta + \\cos^{2}\\theta} \\leq \\frac{2\\sqrt{2}}{3}$",
            "等号成立时 $9\\sin^{2}\\theta = \\cos^{2}\\theta$",
            "$\\Rightarrow \\sin \\theta = \\frac{\\sqrt{10}}{10}$，$\\cos \\theta = \\frac{3\\sqrt{10}}{10}$",
            "$\\Rightarrow P(\\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}, \\frac{\\sqrt{10}}{10})$",
            "综上，$y_{1} - y_{2}$ 的最大值是 $\\frac{2\\sqrt{2}}{3}$"
