        "question": "已知 $a, b, c$ 是非负实数，且 $S = a + 2b + 3c$，$T = a + b^{2} + c^{3}$。(1) 求 $T - S$ 的最小值；(2) 若 $S = 4$，求 $T$ 的最大值。",
        "solution": [
            "(1) 因为 $T - S = b^{2} + c^{3} - 2b - 3c$",
            "又 $b^{2} + 1 \\geq 2b$，$c^{3} + 1 + 1 \\geq 3c$",
            "$\\Rightarrow b^{2} - 2b \\geq -1$，$c^{3} - 3c \\geq -2$",
            "所以 $T - S = b^{2} + c^{3} - 2b - 3c \\geq -3$，当且仅当 $b = c = 1$ 时取等号",
            "(2) 因为 $b^{2} \\leq 2b$，否则 $b > 2 \\Rightarrow 2b > 4$，与 $a + 2b + 3c = 4$ 矛盾",
            "因为 $c^{3} \\leq 3c$，否则 $c > \\sqrt{3}$，与 $a + 2b + 3c = 4$ 矛盾",
            "所以 $T = a + b^{2} + c^{3} \\leq a + 2b + 3c = 4$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["(1) $T - S$ 的最小值为 $-3$；(2) $T$ 的最大值为 $4$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "String",
        "error": null
    },
