    {
        "id": 20210314,
        "subfield": "Number Theory",
        "context": "2021年全国高中数学联合竞赛B1卷加试",
        "question": "已知 $m$，$n$ 是大于1的整数，且 $n$ 不是完全平方数，若 $n^{2} + n + 1$ 被 $m$ 整除，求证：$|m - n| > \\sqrt{3n} - 2$。",
        "solution": [
            "显然 $m \\neq n$",
            "① 若 $m > n$",
            "设 $m = n + t$，$t > 0$",
            "$n + t | n^{2} + n + 1 \\Leftrightarrow n + t | t^{2} - t + 1$",
            "若 $n + t = t^{2} - t + 1$，得 $n = (t - 1)^{2}$ 与题意不符（$n$ 不为完全平方数）",
            "若 $2(n + t) = t^{2} - t + 1$，两边模2，可知 $1 \\equiv 0 \\pmod{2}$，矛盾",
            "故 $3(n + t) \\leq t^{2} - t + 1$",
            "解得 $t \\geq 2 + \\sqrt{3 + 3n} > \\sqrt{3n} - 2$",
            "② 若 $m < n$",
            "设 $m = n - t$，$t > 0$",
            "$n - t | n^{2} + n + 1 \\Leftrightarrow n - t | t^{2} + t + 1$",
            "与 ① 同理",
            "$3(n - t) \\leq t^{2} + t + 1 \\Leftrightarrow t^{2} + 4t + 1 - 3n \\geq 0$",
            "$\\Leftrightarrow t \\geq -2 + \\sqrt{3n + 3}$",
            "得 $-2 + \\sqrt{3n + 3} > \\sqrt{3n} - 2$",
            "证毕"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["见解析"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "String",
        "error": null
    },
